<div class='header-section col-xs-12'></div>
<div class='center'>
  <a href="<%= new_user_registration_url %>" class='btn btn-danger btn-lg'>Sign up Now</a>
</div>

<div class='header-section col-xs-12'></div>
<div class='header-section col-xs-12'></div>
<h3 class='col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 center home_section_header'>How it Works</h3>


<div class='row '>
  <div class='why_container section_block col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1'>
    <div class="section_body">
      <p>
        Instead of reuploading hardsubbed videos, you create playable soft subtitles to get views, shares, comments, followers in your own translation channel or group. The original video owner not only gets free subtitles that he can easily import with one-click, all the traffic that goes to the soft subtitles also goes to the original youtube video. Win-Win for both translators and video producers. 
      </p>

      <br>
      <p>
        See our <a href="/features">list of features</a>
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

